WEBVTT

00:00:58.838 --> 00:01:01.360
But no one ever talked about it.

00:01:02.130 --> 00:01:08.154
If burning fossil fuels was so bad
that it threatened our very existence,

00:01:08.649 --> 00:01:11.278
how could we just continue like before?

00:01:12.263 --> 00:01:14.498
Why were there no restrictions?

00:01:15.030 --> 00:01:17.320
Why wasn't it made illegal?

00:01:18.921 --> 00:01:21.891
To me, that did not add up.

00:01:22.288 --> 00:01:24.297
It was too unreal.

00:01:26.401 --> 00:01:28.978
So when I was 11, I became ill.

00:01:29.250 --> 00:01:31.042
I fell into depression,